An alias is a simple way
of calling something or

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:23.780
someone that has a complex or
funny name.

00:00:23.780 --> 00:00:27.320
For example, say you're a huge,
professional wrestler and

00:00:27.320 --> 00:00:30.340
you want your name to scare
the crap out of your opponent.

00:00:30.340 --> 00:00:33.570
Do you seriously think
Terry Gene Bollea will do?

00:00:33.570 --> 00:00:34.650
Of course not.

00:00:34.650 --> 00:00:38.080
