Hulk Hogan.

00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:41.592
Or you're just starting your
career as a pop singer, but

00:00:41.592 --> 00:00:45.619
your parents bestowed upon you
the aristocratic sounding name of

00:00:45.619 --> 00:00:48.268
Florian Cloud de Bounevialle Armstrong.

00:00:48.268 --> 00:00:50.159
It certainly sounds impressive, but

00:00:50.159 --> 00:00:53.320
your fans will have a hard
time remembering it.

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:56.270
Better go by the tape alias, Dido.

00:00:56.270 --> 00:00:59.700
